{"tid":1096554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話說韓國瑜個樣好似韓復榘","createTime":"2019-04-07T19:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T09:30:04.000Z","uid":202340,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7eea139916ca7d07249895efee929d2c1fef490a","tid":1096554,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T19:12:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181028001097-260407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181028001097-260407&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b6f62fa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181028001097-260407</a><br />\n韓國瑜長相竟神複製抗日鐵血名將<br />\n<br />\n中國時報話韓國瑜似饒國華<br />\n但係我覺得韓國瑜似韓復榘多d, 無論樣貌人格都幾似<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUAnxdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUAnxdO.jpg&h=ee7e4b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Enq3gFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEnq3gFw.jpg&h=52f0e621&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77e94d80f0feb9c91d1e8ff67ea6d8ebceda3b3a","tid":1096554,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3186abe6eaaebea87a5f2c4758857adcf5534df","tid":1096554,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"此後7年多，韓復榘是山東省的統治者。韓復榘同日本秘密建立了聯繫，同時暗殺了原山東軍閥張宗昌。此外，他還驅逐了國民革命軍第十七軍軍長劉珍年，對中國國民黨山東省黨部施壓。由此韓復榘使山東省成為高度自治區域，弱化了國民政府中央對山東省的統治。<br />\n...<br />\n韓復榘在到開封出席軍事會議時，蔣介石指責韓「不發一槍，從黃河北岸，一再向後撤退，繼而放棄濟南、泰安，使後方動搖」，韓復榘聽了蔣介石的話，毫不客氣地頂上去說：「山東丟失是我應負的責任，南京丟失是誰負的責任呢？」<br />\n....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友真係似"},{"pid":"132a6480852d00f6a591ea1988ceb1363605deb3","tid":1096554,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83955d6eeb4cd895e2144da6db521854f11ff754","tid":1096554,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T06:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb07c03ba3f5701a606da3b55e4d25fd9795deff","tid":1096554,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}